@page "/use-cases"
@layout MarketingLayout

<PageTitle>Use Cases — NavTour</PageTitle>
<HeadContent>
    <meta name="description" content="See how sales, marketing, customer success, solution engineers, product marketers, and growth teams use NavTour interactive demos." />
</HeadContent>

<section class="mkt-section" style="padding-bottom:var(--space-16)">
    <div class="mkt-container" style="max-width:680px">
        <h1 class="text-center">Built for every go-to-market team</h1>
        <p class="text-center" style="margin-top:var(--space-5)">Whether you're closing deals, driving conversions, or onboarding customers — NavTour helps your team deliver product experiences that move the needle.</p>
    </div>
</section>

@* Sales *@
<section class="mkt-section" id="sales">
    <div class="mkt-container reveal">
        <div class="mkt-grid mkt-grid-2" style="align-items:center;gap:var(--space-16)">
            <div>
                <p class="mkt-eyebrow">For Sales Teams</p>
                <h2 style="margin-top:var(--space-2)">Close deals faster with interactive demos</h2>
                <p style="margin-top:var(--space-4)">Prospects go cold waiting for live demos. With NavTour, share personalized interactive demos instantly after discovery calls. Every prospect gets a tailored experience with their company name, industry context, and relevant use cases built in. Reps spend less time scheduling and more time selling.</p>
                <p style="margin-top:var(--space-3)">Track which prospects engage most deeply, which steps they revisit, and where they drop off — then use that data to prioritize follow-ups and tailor your pitch. Champions can share the demo internally, accelerating multi-stakeholder deals without requiring additional sales calls.</p>
                <ul class="mkt-benefits">
                    <li>Personalize demos with prospect details via URL params</li>
                    <li>Capture leads directly from the demo experience</li>
                    <li>Track engagement to prioritize follow-ups</li>
                    <li>Enable champions to share demos internally</li>
                    <li>Reduce time-to-demo from days to minutes</li>
                    <li>Integrate with CRM for automatic lead enrichment</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="/solutions/sales" class="mkt-btn mkt-btn-primary" style="margin-top:var(--space-8)">Explore Sales Solution</a>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div class="mkt-placeholder mkt-placeholder-feature">Personalized sales demo with prospect branding</div>
                <div class="mkt-testimonial" style="margin-top:var(--space-6)">
                    <blockquote>"NavTour cut our time-to-demo from 3 days to 5 minutes. Our close rate is up 35% since we started sending personalized demos after every discovery call."</blockquote>
                    <div class="mkt-testimonial-attribution">
                        <div>
                            <div class="mkt-testimonial-name">James Whitfield</div>
                            <div class="mkt-testimonial-role">Sales Director, Pinnacle SaaS</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

@* Marketing *@
<section class="mkt-section-alt" id="marketing">
    <div class="mkt-container reveal">
        <div class="mkt-grid mkt-grid-2" style="align-items:center;gap:var(--space-16)">
            <div>
                <div class="mkt-placeholder mkt-placeholder-feature">Website embed with interactive product tour</div>
                <div class="mkt-testimonial" style="margin-top:var(--space-6)">
                    <blockquote>"Embedding NavTour demos on our landing pages increased conversion by 2.8x. Visitors who interact with a demo are 4x more likely to book a call."</blockquote>
                    <div class="mkt-testimonial-attribution">
                        <div>
                            <div class="mkt-testimonial-name">Maria Santos</div>
                            <div class="mkt-testimonial-role">Head of Demand Gen, Vantage CRM</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p class="mkt-eyebrow">For Marketing Teams</p>
                <h2 style="margin-top:var(--space-2)">Convert more visitors with embedded demos</h2>
                <p style="margin-top:var(--space-4)">Website visitors leave without experiencing your product. Embed interactive demos on landing pages, in email campaigns, and across your website. Turn passive browsing into active product engagement. Every interaction generates intent data your sales team can act on.</p>
                <p style="margin-top:var(--space-3)">Use NavTour demos as the centerpiece of your content strategy. Gate high-value demos to capture leads, embed ungated demos for awareness campaigns, and track which content drives the most pipeline. Replace static screenshots and product videos with experiences that let prospects do, not just watch.</p>
                <ul class="mkt-benefits">
                    <li>Embed demos anywhere with a simple script tag</li>
                    <li>Track engagement and attribute pipeline to demos</li>
                    <li>A/B test demo variants to optimize conversion</li>
                    <li>Gate demos with lead capture forms</li>
                    <li>Retarget engaged viewers with intent data</li>
                    <li>Embed in email campaigns for higher click-through</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="/solutions/marketing" class="mkt-btn mkt-btn-primary" style="margin-top:var(--space-8)">Explore Marketing Solution</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

@* Customer Success *@
<section class="mkt-section" id="cs">
    <div class="mkt-container reveal">
        <div class="mkt-grid mkt-grid-2" style="align-items:center;gap:var(--space-16)">
            <div>
                <p class="mkt-eyebrow">For Customer Success</p>
                <h2 style="margin-top:var(--space-2)">Onboard faster with self-serve product tours</h2>
                <p style="margin-top:var(--space-4)">Onboarding takes too long and support tickets pile up. Create step-by-step product tours that guide new users through setup, feature adoption, and best practices — without scheduling a single call. Scale onboarding from 10 customers to 10,000 without adding headcount.</p>
                <p style="margin-top:var(--space-3)">Monitor completion rates to identify which users are stuck and intervene proactively. Build a library of feature-specific tours that CS managers can assign based on each customer's adoption stage. Drive feature discovery, reduce churn, and increase expansion revenue through guided product education.</p>
                <ul class="mkt-benefits">
                    <li>Build guided walkthroughs with tooltips and hotspots</li>
                    <li>Track completion rates to identify stuck users</li>
                    <li>Reduce onboarding time and support volume</li>
                    <li>Create feature-specific adoption tours</li>
                    <li>Assign tours based on customer lifecycle stage</li>
                    <li>Proactive intervention based on engagement signals</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="/solutions/customer-success" class="mkt-btn mkt-btn-primary" style="margin-top:var(--space-8)">Explore CS Solution</a>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div class="mkt-placeholder mkt-placeholder-feature">Self-serve onboarding tour with step progress</div>
                <div class="mkt-testimonial" style="margin-top:var(--space-6)">
                    <blockquote>"We reduced onboarding calls by 60% after launching NavTour product tours. Customers complete setup 3x faster and our NPS went up 15 points."</blockquote>
                    <div class="mkt-testimonial-attribution">
                        <div>
                            <div class="mkt-testimonial-name">David Park</div>
                            <div class="mkt-testimonial-role">VP of Customer Success, Horizon Ops</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

@* Solution Engineers *@
<section class="mkt-section-alt" id="se">
    <div class="mkt-container reveal">
        <div class="mkt-grid mkt-grid-2" style="align-items:center;gap:var(--space-16)">
            <div class="mkt-placeholder mkt-placeholder-feature">Demo library with vertical-specific templates</div>
            <div>
                <p class="mkt-eyebrow">For Solution Engineers</p>
                <h2 style="margin-top:var(--space-2)">Build reusable demo libraries for every vertical</h2>
                <p style="margin-top:var(--space-4)">Stop rebuilding demos from scratch for every prospect. Create a library of modular, reusable demo templates organized by vertical, use case, and buyer persona. Solution engineers build once, sales reps personalize and send in seconds.</p>
                <p style="margin-top:var(--space-3)">Standardize the demo experience across your org. Ensure every prospect sees the best version of your product, regardless of which rep is running the deal. Version control your demos, track which templates drive the highest engagement, and continuously optimize based on real data.</p>
                <ul class="mkt-benefits">
                    <li>Modular template library organized by vertical</li>
                    <li>Personalization tokens for instant customization</li>
                    <li>Version control and template management</li>
                    <li>Usage analytics to identify top-performing demos</li>
                    <li>Role-based access for template editing vs. sharing</li>
                    <li>Standardize demo quality across the sales org</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

@* Product Marketers *@
<section class="mkt-section" id="pmm">
    <div class="mkt-container reveal">
        <div class="mkt-grid mkt-grid-2" style="align-items:center;gap:var(--space-16)">
            <div>
                <p class="mkt-eyebrow">For Product Marketers</p>
                <h2 style="margin-top:var(--space-2)">Launch features with interactive product experiences</h2>
                <p style="margin-top:var(--space-4)">Feature launches deserve more than a blog post and a screenshot. Create interactive demos that let prospects and customers experience new features firsthand. Embed them in launch emails, landing pages, and help docs to drive adoption from day one.</p>
                <p style="margin-top:var(--space-3)">Build competitive battle cards with side-by-side interactive comparisons. Create industry-specific demo variants that speak directly to each buyer persona. Use engagement data to understand which features resonate most and refine your positioning.</p>
                <ul class="mkt-benefits">
                    <li>Interactive feature launch experiences</li>
                    <li>Industry-specific demo variants</li>
                    <li>Competitive battle cards with live comparisons</li>
                    <li>Engagement data for positioning insights</li>
                    <li>Embeddable demos for docs and knowledge bases</li>
                    <li>Persona-specific messaging built into the demo flow</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="mkt-placeholder mkt-placeholder-feature">Feature launch demo with engagement analytics</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

@* Growth Marketers *@
<section class="mkt-section-alt" id="growth">
    <div class="mkt-container reveal">
        <div class="mkt-grid mkt-grid-2" style="align-items:center;gap:var(--space-16)">
            <div class="mkt-placeholder mkt-placeholder-feature">Growth experiment dashboard with demo variants</div>
            <div>
                <p class="mkt-eyebrow">For Growth Marketers</p>
                <h2 style="margin-top:var(--space-2)">Experiment faster with interactive demo variants</h2>
                <p style="margin-top:var(--space-4)">Interactive demos are your highest-converting content format. Use NavTour to run experiments at scale — test different demo lengths, gate placements, CTA copy, and personalization strategies. Measure impact on pipeline, not just page views.</p>
                <p style="margin-top:var(--space-3)">Integrate demo engagement data with your analytics stack to build attribution models that capture the full buyer journey. Identify which demo experiences drive the most qualified pipeline and double down on what works.</p>
                <ul class="mkt-benefits">
                    <li>A/B test demo length, gates, and CTA placement</li>
                    <li>Attribution tracking across the buyer journey</li>
                    <li>Integration with analytics tools (GA, Segment)</li>
                    <li>Engagement-based retargeting audiences</li>
                    <li>Conversion funnel analysis by demo variant</li>
                    <li>API-driven experimentation at scale</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<CtaSection />
